Class ProxySnifferTransactionHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.proxysniffer.ProxySnifferTransactionHandler

  • public class ProxySnifferTransactionHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    A map of all declared transactions whose times are measured during the load test.

    V5.4-E

        public long addTransaction(java.lang.String transactionName,

        Add a new transaction to the map.
        Parameters:
        transactionName - the unique name of the new transaction
        startDataRecordId - the data record ID of the starting URL
        endDataRecordId - the data record ID of the ending URL, or if the ID is a page break then the transaction ends at the end of the corresponding page
